{"tid":1653373,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"其實我唔明將軍澳捉到鬼單嘢，班手足係點諗","createTime":"2019-10-14T04:57:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T05:11:43.000Z","uid":56682,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"310f52fd0cc42f0d0e4482d860e4095861c921b6","tid":1653373,"uid":56682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T04:57:18.000Z","msg":"事源將軍澳手足在遊行期間捉到鬼<br />\n<br />\n冇打到佢殘廢，條黑警已經算係執到<br />\n<br />\n但最後係佢個袋揾到支伸縮警棍，而個問題就係呢度。<br />\n<br />\n大家執到支伸縮警棍就直接扔落屎渠，雖然最後要逼使批防暴要落去執。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下次如果俾更玩嘢嘅手足再撞到呢種情況<br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">佢地可能會先用一支支狀物體扔落屎渠<br />\n然後同在場記者講警棍扔咗落去<br />\n之後佢地再同popo講<br />\n<br />\n然後支棍佢地可能可能下次攞去冒警<br />\n咁就大撚獲了，你知班popo幾著緊自己啲裝備唔見啦，揾子彈都封成條街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，將佢啲隨身物品扔埋落去，咁就唔係咁好囉。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">本人支持警察，特別呼籲大家千奇唔好咁做</span><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"74fd2cebb08de8f4eab4f5e7428b7fbeeff796aa","tid":1653373,"uid":56682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T04:58:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c46efdc8bc27c3971ea24e52d2dead10e2eddf06","tid":1653373,"uid":56682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T04:59:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a8a56150d4bb4f8e84c915185be4cfaeb11089e4","tid":1653373,"uid":56682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:00:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aeb19273858f510cb0bd5605a70eb79f89f238f7","tid":1653373,"uid":56682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:00:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"33bfb8da17600e8cae261b22f59624e68077ac8e","tid":1653373,"uid":56682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:00:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ae088986268d4982fe04a12ee2aa76e9712f1dec","tid":1653373,"uid":56682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:01:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"82b18db3cc259dbd6e04acfe0ba742abba8fd5dc","tid":1653373,"uid":3249